## Action types & labels

- Machine keys: `inventory.consume_on_job`, `asset.check_out`, `small_tool.adjust`, `job.document_upload`, `timekeeping.approved`
- Display labels: `inventory_action_label()`, `serialized_tool_action_label()`, `small_tool_action_label()` ‚Äî never duplicate strings in pages

## Current state (incremental migration)

| Source | Status |
|--------|--------|
| `qr_scan_events` | Dedicated QR open/success/fail log (`qr_scan_event_service`) |
| `inventory_transactions` | Adapter in `dashboard_item_activity_service` |
| `tool_transactions` | Adapter in `dashboard_item_activity_service` |
| `job_activity_log` / `estimate_activity_log` | Separate tables; not in unified feed yet |
| Small tool moves | No txn log yet ‚Äî add table or `activity_events` on adjust |
| `render_activity_feed` | Shared UI renderer |
| `render_activity_panel` | Detail strip ‚Äî should consume `ActivityRecord` later |

## Rules

- New activity UIs call `list_activity()` (or scoped adapter), not per-page `_fmt_ts` / local feed builders
- Extend `activity_feed_service` / adapters ‚Äî do not add a third feed format
- Domain mutations that users care about should be queryable as activity within one release of the write
